WEBVTT

36:25.680 --> 36:27.280 line:80%
My dearest Mrs. Zhao,

36:27.720 --> 36:30.870 line:80%
it's not a good idea to coerce him
into marrying a butcher.

36:30.870 --> 36:32.470 line:80%
Forced fruit is never sweet.

36:33.160 --> 36:35.640 line:80%
It doesn't matter,
as long as it quenches your thirst.
